{"tid":428370,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個細個以為岩 其實錯既野","createTime":"2017-10-08T04:22:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-25T07:15:54.000Z","uid":13521,"like":1,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"461c53857004d5dd81945ee6be4541580d0cc866","tid":428370,"uid":13521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T04:22:50.000Z","msg":"細個以為 抗日戰爭嗰陣 啲日軍投降係因為義勇軍進行曲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 嚇走咗佢哋"},{"pid":"8b778992ccec72547b9709b2ebd8310a1691482b","tid":428370,"uid":138658,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T04:28:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>細個以為 抗日戰爭嗰陣 啲日軍投降係因為義勇軍進行曲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 嚇走咗佢哋</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2703a820ba321484cc2aea28bd09382b624eed73","tid":428370,"uid":17835,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T04:31:46.000Z","msg":"細個真係信好人有好報，有公義等等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3e0aeb79f4b5a6be1c074f7b4e8c5e9a5583967","tid":428370,"uid":13521,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T04:37:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>細個真係信好人有好報，有公義等等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好少聽第三者有天收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係我覺得好嘅人既運係好啲"},{"pid":"51fd58e692622f9c320ba3aa373d7b9927a123ae","tid":428370,"uid":38047,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T04:38:29.000Z","msg":"細個以為岩係啱。"},{"pid":"83a91d86010da6eeb5a18fbe320e0128592f7bdd","tid":428370,"uid":56240,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T04:42:04.000Z","msg":"以為大個唔驚冇女朋友<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a2fef79ce5b6bee725851d68e0f7f0909d81191","tid":428370,"uid":13521,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T04:50:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以為大個唔驚冇女朋友<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n升中四了，還未試過拍拖，但毒男說：「不緊要，依家努力讀書考好會考，第時有錢你荒（慌）無女？」<br />\n<br />\n結果，毒男克服了一個又一個的考試，升上大學；影畢業相時，發覺好多人都一雙一對，原來大學係撮合情侶既好地方。毒男依然一個，但他說：「不緊要，即將係我踏入社會大展拳腳既時候，亦係我幸福生活既開始！」<br />\n<br />\n毒男努力工作，三年，五年，七年過去了，依然單身。但他終於達成了心願，成為高收入人仕 － 月薪達二萬零五百蚊。<br />\n<br />\n毒男年過三十，開始疑惑：「點解我已經係成功人仕，但仲係無女？」更令他驚訝的是，公司不少女同事都同MK型男拍拖結婚，但那些男人可不是事業型喎，例如，Dorothy既男朋友只係中五畢業既Sales，月薪只有一萬八千蚊，比自己足足少了二千多元！點解？唔係努力讀書成為有錢人就有女既咩？<br />\n<br />\n不知不覺毒男到了中年，身邊已無什麼朋友，自己渡過一個又一個既聖誕節及情人節。<br />\n<br />\n毒男年老了，孤零零一個坐在公園，回想一生：「自己曾得過什麼？女人的身體是怎麼樣的？和女朋友係海邊共渡平安夜既滋味係點架？高登人不是經常留帖話：『後生時唔好浪費時間，第時有錢你荒無女咩！』我照做了，究竟什麼地方出錯？」"},{"pid":"0e0fc1f11d4a3ed1d734014bb4d8747f8a2a2e39","tid":428370,"uid":13521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T05:04:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32b646cc8d3ee1d469581fe9e6c91c00ca77f019","tid":428370,"uid":49136,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T05:19:27.000Z","msg":"電視成日話收視20點30點<br />\n所以以為電視有裝鏡頭<br />\n搞到唔敢係電視前面換衫<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b886023fe07ab4fc40286bd615d6d66beee80e3","tid":428370,"uid":152229,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T05:41:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>電視成日話收視20點30點<br />\n所以以為電視有裝鏡頭<br />\n搞到唔敢係電視前面換衫<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/disl